- Jassie.
- Solo.

616
00:56:21,459 --> 00:56:23,791
Jassie. Jassie.

617
00:56:25,896 --> 00:56:27,659
- Solomon.
- Jassie.

618
00:56:36,440 --> 00:56:37,668
- Solomon.
- Jassie.

619
00:56:37,985 --> 00:56:38,969
Dia nerede?

620
00:56:39,410 --> 00:56:41,207
Dia! Dia!

621
